Qualitek International, Inc. is a significant player offering a comprehensive portfolio of soldering materials and equipment, supporting diverse soldering applications in electronics, automotive, and aerospace industries. SRA Solder specializes in soldering products, including solder paste and fluxes, addressing the evolving needs of the electronics manufacturing sector. ITW EAE is a player providing advanced soldering equipment and solutions for a wide range of applications, ensuring high-quality soldering processes in various industries. Martin SMT Ltd. brings expertise in surface mount technology and soldering equipment, catering to the precise requirements of the electronics and healthcare sectors. JBC Soldering is a renowned name in the industry, offering innovative soldering solutions with a focus on sustainability and efficiency, contributing to sustainable soldering practices in different applications.

